{"type":"article","id":20769,"title":"冒中国人民之大不韪，支持Black Lives Matter","uid":50245,"topics":[28,1,163,442],"contents":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tengbiao/status/1275241007714635783\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">滕彪</a>：“昨天一个美国人和我打电话聊了很长时间。她对这么多中国异议者、维权者的种族主义言论感到非常不解、震惊和伤心。她十几年前开始支持中国的良心犯，做了很多工作。她对其中一位人权活动者照顾有加并寄予厚望。但看到他经常大量转发仇恨言论和仇恨视频，发表种族主义倾向的言论，她难过得哭了。”<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbI3f0pUwAEYMVD?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbI3f0pUwAEYMVD?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbI3f0pUwAEYMVD?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-06-24","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}